  <div class="container-md">
    <h1 class="mb-5 text-center">How to use Vocably in iOS Safari</h1>
    <p>Vocably has been delivered as an iOS Safari extension since March 21st, 2024. It is in Beta, which means the extension might not work as well as on other platforms.</p>

    <p>The Safari extension is available for iOS v17 and further.</p>

    <h2>Enable the extension</h2>

    <p>First, you'll have to install the fresh version of <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/vocably-pro-language-cards/id1641258757" target="_blank">Vocably for iOS</a>.</p>

    <p>After you have installed the app, go to Settings -> Safari -> Extensions and enable Vocably for Safari extension.</p>

    <p>You will also have to allow the extension on vocably.pro website to be able to login into your account.</p>

    <p>
      <video loop autoplay muted controls class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 400px;">
        <source src="assets/ios-safari-extension/enable-extension.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
    </p>

    <p>You can allow the extension on Other Websites, if you trust it. The source code of extension is <a href="https://github.com/vocably/vocably-pro/tree/main/packages/ios-extension" target="_blank">available here</a>.</p>

    <p>If you allowed the extension on Other Website, you can skip the "Allow the extension on a website" step.</p>

    <h2>Allow the extension on a website</h2>

    <p>Open Safari and go to any website. Click the "aA" icon in the address bar and select "Vocably for Safari".</p>

    <p>
      <img src="assets/ios-safari-extension/extension-menu.png" class="figure-img img-fluid" alt="Vocably for Safari in the website menu.">
    </p>

    <h2>Select and look up</h2>

    <p>After you have allowed the extension on the website, you can select any word, click the "Look up" button, and follow the instructions.</p>

    <p>
      <img src="assets/ios-safari-extension/select-and-lookup.png" class="figure-img img-fluid" alt="How to select and look up.">
    </p>

    <p>
      You can always contact us at <a href="mailto:d@vocably.pro">d@vocably.pro</a> if you have any questions. I answer all the emails.
    </p>
